<para>The function enters a loop over the array of containers with the ADC channel information specified in devicetree and checks if the device at index i is ready for usage with call of function device_is_ready. Afterwards the ADC channel of device at index i will be configured by calling function adc_channel_setup_dt provided by the Zephyr ADC API. </para>
